            <thetext>The carousel currently overrides the append method to make sure to update the pagination labels e.g.. Unfortunately, thats not enough because we have other API to add children to container widgets like insertBefore, appendTo, ... 
For such use cases, we have added an event named &quot;childAdded&quot; which catches all the ways a widget can be appended. The carousel should use that event as well to make sure all ways to append a page work the same way.</thetext>
